Friends, Designers, fellow bikers….fellow fitness enthusiasts!  Some may know that I have been very involved rebuilding my local mountain bike trail, Quiet Waters.  We just opened it back to full length after 3 years.  On October 29th, we will host our fund raising race.  All support goes to the trail fund.  If you would like to sponsor, you can get advertising for your company.  Sponsors start at $100.  Thanks for considering, please PM me if you are interested. #mountainbike #floridamtb #floridamountainbiketrails
